  Locus:
    Page: 343
    Verse: 5
Tags:
  - Oneness
---
We go on believing we are separate. We are not—not even for a single
moment. Drop the idea of separation—and the fear of death disappears. If
you become one with the whole, you will live forever. You will go beyond
birth and death.
